(134, 1, '2010-09-24 12:50:13', '2010-09-24 12:50:13', 'Growing businesses present different challenges for the management team. With changing business dynamics and client’s spreading over wider geographies, productivity, motivation and communication become key to success.\r\n\r\nEffective processes and team structure are essential to ensure that communication does not suffer as the business grows. Structuring key elements of the business to improve decision making processes allows the right people to take ownership and drive the organisation. \r\n\r\nTake time to look at the flow of communication in your business and establish structures and processes for maximum benefit. Innovative ideas and solutions often come from the people that do the job. Capturing and using these ideas allows the business to flex and grow.', 'Improve Communication', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'improvecommunication', '', '', '2010-11-01 11:13:16', '2010-11-01 11:13:16', '', 116, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/?page_id=134', 0, 'page', '', 0),
