(116, 1, '2010-09-24 12:43:11', '2010-09-24 12:43:11', 'Established businesses can lack the natural energy they had in the early days. The skills and people needed to start the organisation are not always the ones to build it to the next level. Business leaders often need to change and remove barriers to growth to increase profitability. Building the culture and management team are essential to transform and grow the business. ', 'For Established SME''s', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'for-established-smes', '', '', '2010-10-27 10:15:30', '2010-10-27 10:15:30', '', 62, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/?page_id=116', 2, 'page', '', 0),
