(122, 1, '2010-09-24 12:48:03', '2010-09-24 12:48:03', 'Having a robust business plan is essential to shaping the strategy and direction of your business. Getting this right is fundamental – it takes research, time and tough decision making. \r\n\r\nSherpa provide support and clarity throughout this process to help you define your vision, strategy and business model through to the sales, marketing and recruitment strategy.\r\n\r\nOnce the business plan is in place, the next step is to execute it, to go from a concept to the reality of making sales and generating profit. Sherpa works with you to create tactical action plans with clear objectives, roles and responsibilities to help you make this reality happen quickly and effectively.\r\n\r\nWe coach you and your team throughout the process to transfer vital knowledge and build momentum to create a motivated and dynamic culture in your business. \r\n', 'Business Planning', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'businessplanning', '', '', '2010-10-21 14:36:26', '2010-10-21 14:36:26', '', 109, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/?page_id=122', 0, 'page', '', 0),
