(753, 2, '2010-10-18 13:37:48', '2010-10-18 13:37:48', 'Leading a business can be a lonely place. With ever changing internal and external conditions, prioritising your time spent in the business and on the business is challenging. \r\n\r\nLeading the team and driving the business requires critical decision making. Having the objectivity of a third party such as a non exec or a mentor, helps to keep on track and gives you support to move past tough obstacles and testing times.\r\n\r\n Performance management, restructures leading change are key times when action is needed fast to pull the team into a positive and proactive direction. ', 'Making Tough Decisions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '353-revision-4', '', '', '2010-10-18 13:37:48', '2010-10-18 13:37:48', '', 353, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/353-revision-4.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
