(142, 1, '2010-09-24 12:52:40', '2010-09-24 12:52:40', 'An independent strategic review of your business help identify key issues or opportunities in your business. Sherpa work with you to identify the growth potential and bain your business and provide a road map of how to get there. provides an objective perspective to\r\n\r\nSherpa help define your business objectives, vision and mission to clarify your long-term direction and overall purpose and aspirations. We help you to create an action plan and implement your vision. \r\n\r\n', 'Strategic Review', '', 'pending', 'open', 'open', '', 'strategic-review', '', '', '2010-11-01 09:27:18', '2010-11-01 09:27:18', '', 60, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/?page_id=142', 1, 'page', '', 0),
