(146, 1, '2010-09-24 12:53:08', '2010-09-24 12:53:08', 'Sherpa can provide experienced interim managers in key areas such as finance, sales, operations or management, to provide hands on, specialist support through periods of growth or change in your business. \r\n\r\nA fixed term partnership with an interim manager can strengthen your team by transferring essential skills and experience. We can help embed change, manage teams and make introductions into people who will add value to your business.', 'Interim Management', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'interim-management', '', '', '2010-10-29 15:29:38', '2010-10-29 15:29:38', '', 60, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/?page_id=146', 10, 'page', '', 0),
