(256, 1, '2010-09-27 13:05:13', '2010-09-27 13:05:13', 'Catalyst is a commercialisation programme that helps businesses to evaluate new products and services to find the best commercial opportunity and growth potential. Sherpa work with businesses through the key stages of the commercialisation process to take ideas from concept to the reality of first sale.\r\n\r\nIf you are a start up, entrepreneur or established business with a new product or service to take to market or find investment for, Sherpa Catalyst helps you fast track the process. We work with through the stages of the commercialisation process including:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Market research and feasibility</li>\r\n<li>Feasibility studies</li>\r\n<li>Proof of concept</li>\r\n<li>Business modelling</li>\r\n<li>Market testing</li>\r\n<li>Building the business case</li>\r\n<li>Sales strategy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThorough research into potential routes to market allows you to focus on where you can get traction quickest to prove the concept. Sherpa become part of your team to help gain critical traction to get your business to market.\r\n\r\nCall Sherpa on 0191 211 1995 for a free consultation  and find out how we can help make your concept a reality.', 'Sherpa Catalyst', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sherpa-catalyst', '', '', '2010-11-01 15:07:44', '2010-11-01 15:07:44', '', 0, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress', 0, 'page', '', 0),
