(439, 2, '2010-10-08 11:40:35', '2010-10-08 11:40:35', '\r\nMoney is a major concern for start up businesses and there are many different schemes and sources of funding and finance to apply for at this stage of growth in a business. The problem is researching and navigating the many options and identifying the right one for you.\r\n\r\nMoney is available from various government departments and agencies nationally and locally to support start up businesses, innovation and enterprise. \r\n\r\nFunding should help you achieve your vision and push you in the direction you want to go in, not take you off into a different direction, purely because it fits the criteria. It needs to fit with you current plans and not take your attention away from the day to day basics of sales.\r\n', 'Start Up Funding ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '124-revision-15', '', '', '2010-10-08 11:40:35', '2010-10-08 11:40:35', '', 124, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/124-revision-15.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
