(370, 2, '2010-10-06 09:15:14', '2010-10-06 09:15:14', 'Are you considering raising finance for your business? There are many ways in which you can do this and various finance and funding schemes around.\r\n\r\nThere are also many things you need to consider and it may be that it’s not actually finance you need –you may just need more sales! These are all decisions where it helps to have some objective advice and support. \r\n\r\nYou need to do what is right for you and you business, not what the competition is doing or what seems popular for other businesses. Every business is different, with different needs and potential. Once you have addresses some fundamental questions, the next step is to match the right funding route for you. Some of these options include:\r\n\r\nGovernment funding \r\n\r\nEquity finance\r\n\r\nBusiness Angels \r\n\r\nVC\r\n', 'Raising Finance', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '140-revision-7', '', '', '2010-10-06 09:15:14', '2010-10-06 09:15:14', '', 140, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/140-revision-7.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(330, 2, '2010-10-06 08:35:40', '2010-10-06 08:35:40', 'Finding finance can be a minefield if you don''t know what you''re looking for...\r\n\r\nAre you considering raising finance for your business? There are many ways in which you can do this and various finance and funding schemes around.\r\n\r\nThere are also many things you need to consider and it may be that it’s not actually finance you need –you may just need more sales! These are all decisions where it helps to have some objective advice and support. \r\n\r\nYou need to do what is right for you and you business, not what the competition is doing or what seems popular for other businesses. Every business is different, with different needs and potential. Once you have addresses some fundamental questions, the next step is to match the right funding route for you. Some of these options include:\r\n\r\nGovernment funding \r\n\r\nEquity finance\r\n\r\nBusiness Angels \r\n\r\nVC\r\n', 'Raising Finance', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '140-revision-5', '', '', '2010-10-06 08:35:40', '2010-10-06 08:35:40', '', 140, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/140-revision-5.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
