(342, 2, '2010-10-06 08:42:08', '2010-10-06 08:42:08', 'Growing a business can feel like starting a new business all over again. Growth means change, and change is not always comfortable. Sherpa can help you manage the challenges of growth.\r\n\r\nStrategy\r\n\r\nYou may need a new business plan\r\nA strategic review of your current situation can provide a lot of clarity \r\n\r\nLeadership and Management\r\nAs a business leader, what does your role look like now and what should it be? Often at this stage you need to make the transition from deliverer to the business person. It’s essential for you to free up your time and resource to pursue other ideas that will benefit and help grow the business.\r\n\r\nDelegation and building/growing the team \r\n', 'Grow your business', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '340-revision-2', '', '', '2010-10-06 08:42:08', '2010-10-06 08:42:08', '', 340, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/340-revision-2.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(343, 2, '2010-10-06 08:43:21', '2010-10-06 08:43:21', 'Once a business has reached a critical mass with a strong market position, it''s a good time to consider a more aggressive growth strategy. Moving into new markets provides real opportunities for new revenue streams.\r\n\r\nIdentifying the right products or services and matching them with clients can help businesses scale quickly. Sherpa help identify and engage with new markets from research and feasibility to sale. Moving into new geographical locations provides the opportunity to grow the team and expand operations into new areas. \r\n\r\nIf this is something you are considering, it helps to have support from an experienced advisor to make sure you plan for quick and effective penetration to increase your impact and success in a new sector.\r\n\r\nSherpa help de-risk the situation to get quick wins. We have experience working in a range of markets and geographies with partners and associates and help you move strategically and operationally into new territories.  ', 'Growth Strategy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'growthstrategy', '', '', '2010-10-27 11:32:37', '2010-10-27 11:32:37', '', 113, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress', 0, 'page', '', 0),
