(368, 2, '2010-10-06 09:13:51', '2010-10-06 09:13:51', 'It can be a great help at this stage of business to get some third party advice on your situation. This advice can come from a number of sources but a business coach or mentor is a highly effective way to gain clarity. \r\n\r\nYou have reached the place you have been aiming to get to but the same strategy may no longer work for you. What is it that you need to grow your business to the next stage?\r\n\r\nIt may be that you need to increase sales, grow your team, establish or improve processes\r\n\r\nDepending on the size of your management team you may need expertise in a certain area – sales, finance or operations. \r\n', 'Objective Assessment', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '138-revision-5', '', '', '2010-10-06 09:13:51', '2010-10-06 09:13:51', '', 138, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/138-revision-5.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(369, 2, '2010-10-06 08:36:46', '2010-10-06 08:36:46', 'Finding finance can be a minefield if you don''t know what you''re looking for...\r\n\r\nAre you considering raising finance for your business? There are many ways in which you can do this and various finance and funding schemes around.\r\n\r\nThere are also many things you need to consider and it may be that it’s not actually finance you need –you may just need more sales! These are all decisions where it helps to have some objective advice and support. \r\n\r\nYou need to do what is right for you and you business, not what the competition is doing or what seems popular for other businesses. Every business is different, with different needs and potential. Once you have addresses some fundamental questions, the next step is to match the right funding route for you. Some of these options include:\r\n\r\nGovernment funding \r\n\r\nEquity finance\r\n\r\nBusiness Angels \r\n\r\nVC\r\n', 'Raising Finance', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '140-revision-6', '', '', '2010-10-06 08:36:46', '2010-10-06 08:36:46', '', 140, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/140-revision-6.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
