(378, 2, '2010-10-06 09:04:17', '2010-10-06 09:04:17', 'Having a robust sales strategy and process is essential for successful businesses. \r\n\r\nSherpa provide an intensive sales workshop to work with you to address vital issues where you want to be, what are your core strengths and who are your ideal clients? Workshops include some of the following: \r\n\r\nStrategic review – a holistic overview of you’re the current sales situation – strengths and successes, weaknesses and failures. Where do you want to be? Who do you want to be working with?\r\nSales process – breaking down the process, making it manageable and achievable. Who is involved? How much time do you spend on sales?\r\nIdentify channels to market\r\nEarly market entry sales\r\nFeasibility \r\nConcept development\r\nShaping your offering \r\n\r\nWe will then provide you with an action plan to ensure you stay on track and reach your goals.    \r\n', ' Sales Development', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '151-revision-6', '', '', '2010-10-06 09:04:17', '2010-10-06 09:04:17', '', 151, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/151-revision-6.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(379, 2, '2010-10-06 09:36:00', '2010-10-06 09:36:00', 'Sherpa can provide experienced interim managers in key areas such as finance, sales, operations or management, to provide hands on, specialist support through periods of growth or change in your business. \r\n\r\nA fixed term partnership with an interim manager can strengthen your team by transferring essential skills and experience. We can help embed change, manage teams and make introductions into people who will add value to your business.', 'Interim Management', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '146-revision-5', '', '', '2010-10-06 09:36:00', '2010-10-06 09:36:00', '', 146, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/146-revision-5.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(380, 2, '2010-10-06 09:43:15', '2010-10-06 09:43:15', 'Sherpa offers support throughout all stages of raising finance – preparing for investment, raising finance then coping and managing the growth. \r\n\r\nDetermine your requirements\r\nSo you have made the decision that you need to raise money, but there are many other things to consider which Sherpa can help you with such as recruitment of senior team, strategic partners and early stage client introductions.\r\n\r\nBusiness plan\r\nThere is also a great deal of work to be on at this stage in creating a winning business plan.  Getting your business in order, shaping the offer, financials.\r\n\r\nVC support\r\nFinding the right funding or VC, size of investment, which industry, meeting their requirements. \r\n\r\nPost finance\r\nA stage people do not always acknowledge when the main focus is winning the money. ', 'Finance & Venture Capital ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '149-revision-7', '', '', '2010-10-06 09:43:15', '2010-10-06 09:43:15', '', 149, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/149-revision-7.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
