(405, 2, '2010-11-01 14:55:46', '2010-11-01 14:55:46', 'Sherpa Clinic is a one day workshop designed to diagnose any barriers to growth and identify potential opportunities in your business. Sherpa Clinic gives businesses the opportunity to have a comprehensive review of their current business strategy, operations and team. \n\nSherpa facilitate the workshop in a boardroom format, working with the business owner and management team to take stock of the fundamentals. Sherpa Clinic provides a holistic overview and analysis of key areas of the business including:\n\n<ul>\n<li>Strategy</li> \n<li>Sales and customers</li> \n<li>Finances</li>\n<li>Operations</li> \n<li>People</li> \n</ul>\n\nSherpa Clinic provides third party objectivity and the ability to take a step back and make informed decisions on the current and future position of the business. It''s sometimes difficult to recognise when your business is not fulfilling its potential or how you are going to tackle it if you do. \n\nContact Sherpa on to see how we can help you realise the potential in your business and provide you with a plan of action to reach\n\n', 'Sherpa Clinic', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '252-autosave', '', '', '2010-11-01 14:55:46', '2010-11-01 14:55:46', '', 252, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/252-autosave.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
