(412, 2, '2010-10-06 08:37:05', '2010-10-06 08:37:05', 'Growing businesses face a range of challenges. As a business grows, different problems and opportunities demand different solutions - what worked a year ago might not be the best approach now. Effective management is required and a possible new business plan. Learn how to train and delegate to conquer this stage of development.', 'For Growing Businesses', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '113-revision-16', '', '', '2010-10-06 08:37:05', '2010-10-06 08:37:05', '', 113, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/113-revision-16.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
