(416, 2, '2010-10-06 13:51:32', '2010-10-06 13:51:32', 'Applying the right sales strategy can often be the difference between success and failure. To improve your chances, it’s essential to identify and focus on the most effective routes to market for your business. \r\n\r\nInvest time and resource into researching your potential markets and understanding their requirements to give your business the best chance of success. This vital information helps you refine your offer and define pricing models, service, delivery, sales channels and marketing plans. \r\n\r\nEven with a great product you need to target the right customers and continue to refine the offer so that when it comes to launch, your sales strategy is focused and informed, giving you higher levels of traction.  \r\n\r\nSherpa work with business on the commercialisation of products and services, developing the strategy and plan to help you find the best markets, identify growth areas and develop strategic alliances that can make things move quickly. \r\n', 'Routes to market', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'routestomarket', '', '', '2010-10-26 15:52:54', '2010-10-26 15:52:54', '', 109, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress', 2, 'page', '', 0),
