(468, 2, '2010-10-08 13:24:47', '2010-10-08 13:24:47', 'Growing businesses present different challenges for the management team. With changing business dynamics and client''s spreading over wider geographies, productivity, motivation and communication become key to sucess. \r\n \r\nStructuring the key elements of the business and mile stones allows the right people to take ownership and drive within the organisation. Innovative ideas and solutions often come from the people that do the job. Capturing and using these ideas allow the business to flex and grow.', 'Improve Communication', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '134-revision-6', '', '', '2010-10-08 13:24:47', '2010-10-08 13:24:47', '', 134, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/134-revision-6.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
