(532, 2, '2010-10-13 14:11:09', '2010-10-13 14:11:09', 'Entrepreneurs grow businesses with natural enthusiasm, desire and energy.  With increasing demands on time, it can be difficult to life your head away from something that you are too close too.  The tough questions of seeing where you add the most value and what the business needs to move up a gear.  With more people in a an organisation brings more complexity and challenges internally.  Focussing the business and the leader on what the business needs and what they need to be allows the business to keep focussed and able to deliver results through empowered culture of ownership.\r\n \r\nStep back away from being sucked into emails, admin issues and areas of the business where there are better people in the organisation to fix the problems and create solutions, allowing the business to blossom.\r\n \r\nThey say it takes 2.7 CEO''s, to take a business global.  Understanding and keeping a transformational role allows the entrepreneur to add value and delegate and recruit according to what the business needs and needs to be successful.\r\n \r\nWhen you start you have to do everything the business needs, when you are a leader you have be everything the business needs.\r\n', 'Manage Your Time ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '130-revision-5', '', '', '2010-10-13 14:11:09', '2010-10-13 14:11:09', '', 130, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/130-revision-5.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(614, 2, '2010-10-21 10:43:23', '2010-10-21 10:43:23', 'Entrepreneurs grow businesses with natural enthusiasm, desire and energy. With increasing demands on time, it can be difficult to prioritise and delegate away from something you are so close to. \r\n\r\nThere are tough questions to answer and decisions to be made to see where you add the most value and what the business needs to move up a gear. A growing business with an increasing head count brings new levels of complexity and internal challenges. Third party objectivity can help you take a step back from the day to day emails, administrative and staff issues to see the areas of the business that other people are better placed to solve problems and create solutions, allowing the business to blossom.\r\n\r\nSherpa works with the management team and the business leader to define what they need to be and what they need to focus on to drive and manage the business. Mentoring and coaching brings clarity to the team and the individual to deliver results and brings a culture of empowerment and ownership.\r\n\r\nUnderstanding and keeping a transformational role allows the entrepreneur to add value and delegate according to what the business needs to be successful. When you start a business you have to do everything the business needs, when you are a leader you have be everything the business needs.\r\n', 'Manage Your Time ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '130-revision-9', '', '', '2010-10-21 10:43:23', '2010-10-21 10:43:23', '', 130, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/130-revision-9.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
