(534, 2, '2010-10-13 14:00:38', '2010-10-13 14:00:38', 'The quality of a good management team is the cornerstone of a successful business that has the ability to scale and cope with the growth.  Going the through the self discovery of the business leaders key strengths and awareness of what the team needs to be successful.   Look at gaps and profiling the right candidates is key to growth and coping with the growth. \r\n \r\nBusinesses involved in finance raising often need key stengths to balance the team and gain traction.  A review of the stategy allows the business to look at where it it is and build the action plan to reach it''s aspirations.  Boardroom simulations allows the business to focus on sales led busineses with a process improvement culture. \r\n \r\nAs businesses grow they can become dysfunctional without the ability to execute the business plan.  With an increased pressure for increased sales, imporeved products and market opportunites keep the business focussed on what makes money and the financial control to kepp the business profitable.\r\n \r\nSherpa focuss on keeping the management team focussed on closind deals, building the brand, delivering first class product and service, with a stroing process and fiancial control to ensure business grow and are able to cope with it.', 'Organisation Structure', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '132-revision-5', '', '', '2010-10-13 14:00:38', '2010-10-13 14:00:38', '', 132, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/132-revision-5.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(609, 2, '2010-10-21 10:34:24', '2010-10-21 10:34:24', 'As businesses grow they can become dysfunctional and lose the focus and ability to execute the business plan. Sherpa help the management team stay focussed on creating opportunities, closing deals, building the brand and delivering first class products and services, with strong control on processes and finance to ensure business growth.\n\nAn effective and well balanced management team is the cornerstone of a successful business, but more importantly to ensure the business can scale and cope with growth. Sherpa takes business leaders through a self discovery process to indentify key strengths and create awareness of what the team needs to be successful. We look at skills gaps and profile the right candidates to build the team.\n\nA strategy review allows you to see where the business is and build an action plan to reach your aspirations. It can also be very valuable to have a third party presence in board meetings to help challenge decisions and drive activity. \n\n', 'Organisation Structure', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '132-autosave', '', '', '2010-10-21 10:34:24', '2010-10-21 10:34:24', '', 132, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/132-autosave.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
