(583, 2, '2010-10-12 13:26:56', '2010-10-12 13:26:56', 'Sherpa offers support throughout all stages of raising finance – preparing for investment, raising finance then coping and managing the growth. \r\n\r\nDetermine your requirements\r\nSo you have made the decision that you need to raise money, but there are many other things to consider which Sherpa can help you with such as recruitment of senior team, strategic partners and early stage client introductions.\r\n\r\nBusiness plan\r\nThere is also a great deal of work to be on at this stage in creating a winning business plan.  Getting your business in order, shaping the offer, financials.\r\n\r\nVC support\r\nFinding the right funding or VC, size of investment, which industry, meeting their requirements. \r\n\r\nPost finance\r\nA stage people do not always acknowledge when the main focus is winning the money. ', 'Finance & Venture Capital ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '149-revision-11', '', '', '2010-10-12 13:26:56', '2010-10-12 13:26:56', '', 149, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/149-revision-11.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
