(674, 2, '2010-10-25 15:20:53', '2010-10-25 15:20:53', 'Are you considering raising finance for your business? There are many ways in which you can do this and various finance and funding schemes around.\n\nThere are many things you need to consider but the first thing you need to think about is why you need the finance –it may be that you just need more sales! These are all decisions where it helps to have some objective advice and support. You need to do what is right for you and your business, not what the competition is doing.\n\nEvery business is different, with different needs and potential. Sherpa can help you address some of these fundamental questions. The next step is to find the right funding route for you. \n\nThere are various sources of financing your business with varying degrees of risk and impact. Sherpa can help you navigate, understand and evaluate the options including venture capital, angel investment, seed funding, debt finance, loans, grant and credits.', 'Raising Finance', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '140-autosave', '', '', '2010-10-25 15:20:53', '2010-10-25 15:20:53', '', 140, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/140-autosave.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
