(681, 2, '2010-10-06 12:34:52', '2010-10-06 12:34:52', 'Growing a business can feel like starting a new business all over again. Growth means change, and change is not always comfortable. Sherpa can help you manage the challenges of growth.\r\n\r\nStrategically it might be time for a new business plan. A strategic review of your current situation can provide a lot of clarity \r\n\r\nAs a business leader, what does your role look like now and what should it be? Often at this stage you need to make the transition from deliverer to the business person. It’s essential for you to free up your time and resource to pursue other ideas that will benefit and help grow the business. Leadership and Management\r\n\r\n\r\nDelegation and building/growing the team \r\n\r\nEstablishing processes\r\n', 'Managing Growth', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '340-revision-7', '', '', '2010-10-06 12:34:52', '2010-10-06 12:34:52', '', 340, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/340-revision-7.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(682, 2, '2010-10-25 16:17:09', '2010-10-25 16:17:09', 'Growing a business can feel like starting a new business all over again. Growth means change, and change is not always comfortable. Sherpa can help you manage the challenges of growth.\r\n\r\nStrategically it might be time for a new business plan. A strategic review of your current situation can provide a lot of clarity and establish a new focus and direction to form the basis of a new plan for growth or exit. \r\n\r\nAs a business leader, what does your role look like now and what should it be? At this stage you need to make the transition from deliverer to the business person. It’s essential for you to free up your time and resource to pursue other ideas that will benefit and help grow the business. Sherpa work with business leaders on this self realisation process to enable you to understand your strengths, where you need to improve and what you need to let go of.\r\n\r\nBeing a manager requires the ability to delegate and get the best out of your team. Building a balanced and structured team of people with the right skills is essential to take the business forward. ', 'Managing Growth', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '340-revision-8', '', '', '2010-10-25 16:17:09', '2010-10-25 16:17:09', '', 340, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/340-revision-8.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
