(713, 2, '2010-10-06 09:14:17', '2010-10-06 09:14:17', 'It can be a great help at this stage of business to get some third party advice on your situation. This advice can come from a number of sources but a business coach or mentor is a highly effective way to gain clarity. \r\n\r\nYou have reached the place you have been aiming to get to but the same strategy may no longer work for you. What is it that you need to grow your business to the next stage?\r\n\r\nIt may be that you need to increase sales, grow your team, establish or improve processes\r\n\r\nDepending on the size of your management team you may need expertise in a certain area – sales, finance or operations. \r\n', 'Objective Assessment', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '138-revision-6', '', '', '2010-10-06 09:14:17', '2010-10-06 09:14:17', '', 138, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/138-revision-6.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(714, 2, '2010-10-26 16:55:09', '2010-10-26 16:55:09', 'As the manager of a growing business, you have made it through the tough start up years and reached the stage of business that you have strived hard to get to. But what do you need to do to grow your business to the next stage? Is the business reaching its full potential? Is it time for a new strategy and direction?\n\nTaking time out to take stock of where you are against your current vision and plan is essential, but something people rarely make time for. Third party advice from a business coach or mentor is a highly effective way to gain clarity and challenge these key business decisions. Often you can be too close and emotionally attached to the business to look at the situation objectively.\n\nSherpa can help you unlock the potential in your business and identify growth opportunities. A strategic review is a proactive way to fully realise where you are and where you want to go. Looking at sales, customers, finances, operations and the team helps revisit your vision and strategy. \n', 'Objective Assessment', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '138-autosave', '', '', '2010-10-26 16:55:09', '2010-10-26 16:55:09', '', 138, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/138-autosave.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
