(718, 2, '2010-10-26 14:35:37', '2010-10-26 14:35:37', 'The business plan is the first step, but making sure you deliver it is another matter. The reality of how you will meet your objectives, hit sales targets and grow your business requires motivation, focus and a lot of effort.\r\n\r\nIt’s essential that you plan, track and manage progress at this early stage of business growth. Short term, tactical goals are key to measuring progress and success. It’s very easy to lose focus to other areas of the business and get into a comfort zone. \r\n\r\nSherpa work with you to create a tactical action plan with clear direction and accountability for measured success. We mentor and support you through the process to keep you on track, focusing on the priorities to fast track your business growth. Having an experienced mentor is a great advantage to provide vital skills and knowledge for your personal development.', 'Making It Happen', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '126-revision-16', '', '', '2010-10-26 14:35:37', '2010-10-26 14:35:37', '', 126, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/126-revision-16.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
