(729, 2, '2010-10-27 11:08:51', '2010-10-27 11:08:51', 'Once a business has reached a critical mass with a strong market position, it''s a good time to consider a more aggressive growth strategy. Moving into new markets provides real opportunities for new revenue streams.\r\n\r\nIdentifying the right products or services and matching them with clients can help businesses scale quickly. Sherpa help identify and engage with new markets from research and feasibility to sale. Moving into new geographical locations provides the opportunity to grow the team and expand operations into new areas. \r\n\r\nIf this is something you are considering, it helps to have support from an experienced advisor to make sure you plan for quick and effective penetration to increase your impact and success in a new sector.\r\n\r\nSherpa help de-risk the situation to get quick wins. We have experience working in a range of markets and geographies with partners and associates and help you move strategically and operationally into new territories.  ', 'Growth Strategy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '343-revision-4', '', '', '2010-10-27 11:08:51', '2010-10-27 11:08:51', '', 343, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/343-revision-4.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
