s and you can easily lose focus on the actual business. Having short term, expert support throughout the process helps you stay on track while staying focused on the business and the execution of the plan. We add value to help you recruit a senior team, find strategic partners and make early stage client introductions.\r\n', 'Investment & Venture Capital ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '149-revision-51', '', '', '2010-10-29 11:17:20', '2010-10-29 11:17:20', '', 149, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/149-revision-51.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(877, 2, '2010-10-29 10:43:50', '2010-10-29 10:43:50', 'A robust sales strategy and process is essential for successful businesses. Sherpa provide a number of solutions to focus your sales strategy to maximise profit margins and growth. We get back to the basics to answer the vital questions of where you want to be, what are your core strengths and who are your ideal clients? This information is essential to shape your sales strategy. We will then provide you with an action plan to ensure you stay on track and reach your goals. Some of the specific areas sales development services include:\r\n\r\n<strong>Sales review:</strong> a holistic overview of your current sales situation – strengths, successes, weaknesses and failures. Where do you want to be? Who do you want to work with? What do you want to be famous for? \r\n<strong>Sales process:</strong> breaking down the process, making it targeted, manageable and achievable. Who is involved? How much time do you spend on sales? \r\n<strong>Channels to market:</strong> are you reaching your market potential? Sherpa help you define new markets \r\n<strong>Sales techniques:</strong> tools and techniques to improve your selling skills. Pitching, persuasion, negotiation and deal making.\r\n\r\n', ' Sales Development', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '151-revision-20', '', '', '2010-10-29 10:43:50', '2010-10-29 10:43:50', '', 151, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/151-revision-20.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
