(879, 2, '2010-10-29 14:46:52', '2010-10-29 14:46:52', '<strong>Background: </strong>YourFilm are an owner-managed film production company based in Gateshead. They were looking to increase the profitability of their company and establish growth within untapped market areas.\r\n\r\nSherpa mentored YourFilm and managed the implementation of a cohesive sales strategy that led the business to double its turnover. YourFilm have also now established a subsidiary company – We3 – targeted specifically at the commercial market.\r\n\r\n<strong>Solution:</strong> Sherpa worked with YourFilm to establish their strengths and growth potential to provide a clear vision for strategic sales development. \r\n\r\n<strong>Strategic review</strong>\r\nSherpa undertook a strategic review of the business, identifying areas which needed to be focused on to increase their profitability, including an operational review of roles within the business. As a small growing business it was essential to  clarify roles and responsibilities to maximise the effectiveness of the team. \r\n\r\n<strong>Sales strategy</strong>\r\nA focused sales strategy was developed to ensure the company produced a balanced portfolio of work, encompassing the Corporate/ TV/ Commercial fields of film production. The definition of roles within the business allowed the owners to focus on specific areas of individual expertise. \r\n\r\n<strong>Mentoring</strong>\r\nSherpa were involved in a mentoring capacity with YourFilm over a period of nine months to transfer essential skills and help embed the sales strategy. The ongoing mentoring programme also ensured that the desired outcomes of the strategic review kept in focus.', 'YourFilm', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'yourfilm', '', '', '2010-11-01 12:03:24', '2010-11-01 12:03:24', '', 58, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress', 2, 'page', '', 0),
