(901, 2, '2010-10-29 10:41:59', '2010-10-29 10:41:59', 'Sherpa can provide experienced interim managers in key areas such as finance, sales, operations or management, to provide hands on, specialist support through periods of growth or change in your business. \r\n\r\nA fixed term partnership with an interim manager can strengthen your team by transferring essential skills and experience. We can help embed change, manage teams and make introductions into people who will add value to your business.', 'Interim Management', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '146-revision-8', '', '', '2010-10-29 10:41:59', '2010-10-29 10:41:59', '', 146, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/146-revision-8.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(902, 2, '2010-10-29 10:40:51', '2010-10-29 10:40:51', 'A business mentor or coach helps you reach your goals and gives you motivation and encouragement to keep on track. One to one support adds value to your business by helping you to set goals, facilitate clear decision-making and achieve peak performance. \r\n\r\nIf you are starting out in business, it helps to have someone with more experience to share their knowledge and keep you on the right track. Maybe you have a great idea for a business but needs a bit of guidance to turn it into a successful and profitable venture. Or maybe you have been in business for a while and feel you need to grow personally and develop or improve in some area.\r\n\r\nMany successful entrepreneurs and executives attribute their success to a business mentor or coach giving them support and guidance to achieve specific goals.\r\n\r\nTop athletes and sports people could not achieve the level of success or results without a coach so why would it be any different in business. \r\n\r\nThe relationship between the entrepreneur and mentor involves a lot of trust from both sides, but the result of having someone with business experience to guide you through tough decisions and offer tactical support of how to improve your business, is invaluable\r\n\r\nIt’s a two-way communication process to share their wealth of skills, experience and expertise with those hungry for knowledge and guidance.', ' Mentoring & Coaching', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '144-revision-18', '', '', '2010-10-29 10:40:51', '2010-10-29 10:40:51', '', 144, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/144-revision-18.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
