(922, 2, '2010-10-29 15:14:39', '2010-10-29 15:14:39', '<strong>Background:</strong> YourFilm are an owner-managed film production company based in Gateshead. They were looking to increase the profitability of their company and establish growth within untapped market areas.\r\n\r\n<strong>Outcome:</strong> Sherpa have been involved in a mentoring capacity for 9 months, overseeing the implementation of a cohesive sales strategy and an organisational development programme. In this period, the business turnover has doubled. YourFilm have also set up a subsidiary company, We3tv- directing their services specifically at the commercial market.\r\n\r\n<strong>The Solution:</strong> \r\n\r\n<strong>Strategic review</strong>\r\nSherpa undertook a strategic review of the business, identifying areas which needed to be focused on to increase their profitability. The business owners understood the need for change and engaged in an operational review to clarify roles within the business. \r\n\r\n<strong>Sales strategy</strong>\r\nA focused sales strategy was developed to ensure the company produced a balanced portfolio of work, encompassing the Corporate/ TV/ Commercial fields of film production.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThe definition of roles with the business has allowed the owners to focus on specific areas of individual expertise. The ongoing mentoring programme has ensured that the desired outcomes of the strategic review kept in focus.\r\n\r\n', 'YourFilm', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '879-revision-10', '', '', '2010-10-29 15:14:39', '2010-10-29 15:14:39', '', 879, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/879-revision-10.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
