(996, 2, '2010-10-29 10:51:56', '2010-10-29 10:51:56', 'Good financial information allows you to make informed decisions on the business and the people within it.\r\n\r\nThe production of management accounts is one thing, but then focussing on the key points within the detail is often something that goes missing.\r\n\r\nSherpa''s part time FD solution is hugely valueable for the those business that need more than numbers.  What do the numbers mean? where''s the focus? tough questions in the boardroom and the challenge to make informed decisions for the good of the business.\r\n\r\nThis solution has been particularly useful for SME''s with incomplete boards with FD being the nice to have opposed the fundamental important. For a lot of entreprenuers managing the numbers is not best use of time.  So give it to an expert while you get on with the fun stuff growing the business and delivering.\r\n', 'Finance Management', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '318-revision-13', '', '', '2010-10-29 10:51:56', '2010-10-29 10:51:56', '', 318, 'http://www.sherpabusinessconsultancy.com/wordpress/business-consultancy/318-revision-13.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
